Muchidzidzo chidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[rutsazanisi]] (equator), mutsetse unopangidza panosangana uso hweurungano nemutsendo unocheka akiso yekuzeya ''(axis of rotation)'' kweurungano yacho negonya re 90<sup>o</sup>. Kureva kuti mutsendo uyu wakaita mutwi neakiso. Chimwe chinoonekwa kuti [[goko rehuremu]] ''(centre of mass)'' yeurungano iri pamutsendo iwoyu zvakare.  Vara guru rinoshandiswa kana pari kutsangudzwa Rutsazanisi rweRinopasi, (Earth).

Takatarisana neRinopasi, [[Rutsazanisi]] mutsetse wekufungidzira une nhambwe dzakaenzana kubva ku[[North Pole]] kusvika ke[[South Pole]] panzvimbo dzose. Mutsetse uyu unocheka urungano yeRinopasi kuita zvikamu zviviri zvakaenzana.

